<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT42">
<l>ceṉṟu vaṇaṅkumiṉō cēṇuyar vēṅkaṭattai</l>
<l>niṉṟu viṉaikeṭukkum nīrmaiyā leṉṟuṅ</l>
<l>kaṭikkamala nāṉmukaṉuṅ kaṇmūṉṟat tāṉu</l>
<l>maṭikkamala miṭṭēttu maṅku.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Will you not go [and] worship the very lofty Vēṅkaṭam?</l>
<l>Due to [its] nature that constantly destroys karman,</l>
<l>The four-faced [Brahmā] on the fragrant lotus and the three-eyed [Śiva],</l>
<l>forever praise [Him] there, placing lotuses [at His] feet.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
